00:12:57,308 --> 00:13:03,034
dos iz gevezn shpeter vos zenen zey avekgeforn. frier z- iz gevezn veynik mentshn vos zenen avek

237
00:13:03,034 --> 00:13:08,064
f- shpeter az m'hot undz shoyn genumen in ge- in lager arayn, in geto, in lager

