00:13:35,091 --> 00:13:39,422
ikh red nokh for dem geto, hot men, iz nisht geven keyn yidishe

248
00:13:38,938 --> 00:13:42,880
neyn, dos iz gevezn in insh- in, in Kroke, vu ikh hob gevoynt.

249
00:13:43,123 --> 00:13:45,187
hot men gemuzt ales opgebn

