258
00:14:16,448 --> 00:14:19,398
⟨BUT⟩ nokh alts nisht gevolt oy- oysshnaydn di bord.

259
00:14:19,398 --> 00:14:21,698
ABER shpeter, leyder, hot er gemuzt opshnaydn.

260
00:14:21,666 --> 00:14:26,250
