00:14:37,765 --> 00:14:41,724
keyn TRAM hot men nisht gemegt forn. keyn tsug hot men nisht gemegt forn.

266
00:14:42,169 --> 00:14:47,237
⟨BUT⟩ m'hot nisht gemegt geyn tsu goyishe gesheftn aynkoyfn, nor alts tsvishn ⟨do⟩ tsvishn yidn.

267
00:14:47,237 --> 00:14:54,634
az s'hot men gevolt geyn oyf di lange gas, gevezn goyishe gesheftn azoy vi UNK ⟨WIELKY⟩ vos iz geven tshokolade vos hot men UNK dort gekoyft

268
00:14:54,943 --> 00:14:56,405
hot men nisht gemegt geyn.

269
00:14:56,867 --> 00:15:01,248
un vi iz geven di REAKTION fun di nisht yidishe bafelkerung, di

270
00:15:01,086 --> 00:15:02,767
oh, zey hobn ⟨es⟩ gehat hanoe.

271
00:15:03,297 --> 00:15:07,837
zey hobn g- hanoe. zey hobn gezogt az dos ⟨iz⟩ gevezn yidishe hayzer

272
00:15:07,837 --> 00:15:09,297
⟨un⟩ undzere gasn.

273
00:15:09,297 --> 00:15:11,177
yetst vet zayn undzere gas oy-

274
00:15:11,177 --> 00:15:14,366
gasn, un zeyer h- nisht keyn, nisht keyn yidn.

275
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:19,470
yidishe h- hayzer ⟨un⟩ zeyere gasn zenen ⟨zey⟩ gevezn.

276
00:15:19,470 --> 00:15:22,270
un shpeter hobn zey gezogt az dos vet zayn undzere gasn

277
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:24,396
undzere gasn, undzere hayzer.

278
00:15:24,396 --> 00:15:26,190
oh, zey hobn gehat hanoe mit dem.

279
00:15:26,719 --> 00:15:28,215
zey hobn gehat hanoe.

280
00:15:28,980 --> 00:15:33,277
un vos, vi hot zikh ongehoybn di shmue fun dem

281
00:15:33,351 --> 00:15:36,618
tsu geyn in a geto? gedenkt ir fun dem?

282
00:15:35,325 --> 00:15:41,515
yo. zey hobn gezogt az zey makhn dos a plats far undz, a spetsyeln PODGORZE, a spetsyel plats

283
